            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!)<strong> </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Sprinkle in the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock mix </strong>and add the <strong>tomato paste</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 2 min or until the mince<strong> </strong>is browned all over</p><p>Add the <strong>basmati rice </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1685399587385-x200.jpg",
