            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and 350ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice cooked</p><p>Tip: Add a splash more water if it's looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
