        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>black beans</strong> and <strong>coriander stalks</strong> then cook for a further 2 min or until the beans are warmed through – this is your <strong>Mexican-style meat-free mince rice</strong></p>",
